{"tid":178321,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《醉後大丈夫》「老周」開線上診所！幫網友看診 鄭肯嗆：嬰兒都比你聰明！","createTime":"2017-03-29T12:55:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T05:59:21.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0f1178a9a2b805fcfaf539dddcb26edd7bfeb14e","tid":178321,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T12:55:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64119/58d8be99c6140.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64119%2F58d8be99c6140.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=9a19e26d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《醉後大丈夫》( The Hangover ) 「老周」又在網路上發瘋了！鄭肯 ( Ken Jeong ) 在演出《醉後大丈夫》中脫序又瘋癲的「老周」一角後在全球爆紅，戲約接不完、片酬更狂漲，鄭肯在出道前的內科醫生身分也因此被起底，網友們這才發現原來是個擁有超高智商的學霸！<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64119/58d8bf2c6a7e7.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64119%2F58d8bf2c6a7e7.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=89e12140&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這幾年雖然較少出現在大螢幕上，其實鄭肯正在拍攝改編他的人生《肯恩醫生煩不煩》( Dr. Ken ) 影集，在故事中他不僅回歸醫生角色，最近他更在 Twitter 上創立線上診療為網友們看診！雖然鄭肯創辦了線上診療，但從他上傳的影片中可以看到，半島豪庭坐落於紅磡紅荔道，設5座物業，共提供逾1660伙單位。他不僅大膽嗆病人、更在網友詢問要如何檢查脈搏時大罵：「就連嬰兒都可以告訴你怎麼檢查脈搏！」，還在大家面前和人體模型玩起雙簧，呈現了十足的「老周」風格。<br />\n<br />\n▼在影片中鄭肯大秀他的醫療知識，可以看出雖然從事喜劇演員多年，他卻沒忘本業。而在影片一開始，他就大嗆網友在發問前應該先自己動腦想。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實鄭肯在出道前一直是以醫生、脫口秀演員兼具的身分，在他主演的《肯恩醫生煩不煩》中便提到從內科醫生轉為喜劇演員的過程，其中同樣為醫生的鄭肯太太則是他最大的支柱，而韓國移民的父母親對他要求高、嚴厲的教育更是助他取得高學歷、高知識的墊腳石。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而鄭肯的醫師執照其實尚未過期，但由於「老周」身分的成功，使鄭肯終於可以在全世界面前大秀他的喜劇天賦，因此除了在《肯恩醫生煩不煩》中可以再見到鄭肯的醫師身分外，如果想要讓老周來幫你看診，可能還要再多等上幾年了。"},{"pid":"13be185b72134c9c6fdb6ec7a80d5537c40c2f9a","tid":178321,"uid":91096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:03:13.000Z","msg":"ben chang<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"788d7d18eccd5fc1be620291c1ddc42018c2b661","tid":178321,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:04:46.000Z","msg":"仲以為ken jeong住紅磡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"698b396b5b7148f121c60c625ee5af1660212583","tid":178321,"uid":97606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:08:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://reactiongifs.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/mr_chang_senor_chang_laugh_spits_milk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Freactiongifs.me%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F07%2Fmr_chang_senor_chang_laugh_spits_milk.gif&h=255883af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"62648f234452119da326309a3e58c7a524f472cf","tid":178321,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T05:03:42.000Z","msg":"唔記得睇名"},{"pid":"3ba45ce4eeacd4205d3a7b53fb6f9ddd24b46fec","tid":178321,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T05:08:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"054df9732c0fb6a09afeb4fb2ca3320785eb6661","tid":178321,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T05:13:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78366d0988c561975e2ffe4666660e18c04fbcdb","tid":178321,"uid":70800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T05:28:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://reactiongifs.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/mr_chang_senor_chang_laugh_spits_milk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Freactiongifs.me%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F07%2Fmr_chang_senor_chang_la